k:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pzz1665702659433.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pzz1665702659433.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pzz1665702659433.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pzz1665702659433\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Creates one or more archive files based on object, library, and language.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__topic_d177065e1_d177066e1_d177067e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__p_d177068e1_d177069e1_d177070e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Switches</var>} <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">split</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ArchiveFile</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">$RSO</code> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Options</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__section_tp4_hw1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d950463e75\">Switches</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__ul_c3y_nw1_dcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d53969e1_d53970e1_d53971e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iil1665702549278.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iil1665702549278.html\" title=\"Specify the assignment file used by the application.\">/asn</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d53972e1_d53973e1_d53974e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zvr1665702548679.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zvr1665702548679.html\" title=\"Specify the working directory for a Uniface application.\">/dir</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d53975e1_d53976e1_d53977e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tsb1719651708881.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tsb1719651708881.html\" title=\"Return the natural logarithm of X (log e X).\">$log</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d53978e1_d53979e1_d53980e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gys1665702658931.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gys1665702658931.html\" title=\"Puts messages in the specified log file.\">/plg</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d53981e1_d53982e1_d53983e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"unz1665702549564.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/unz1665702549564.html\" title=\"Specify the types of messages sent to the message frame or log file.\">/pri</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d53984e1_d53985e1_d53986e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wsn1665702659009.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wsn1665702659009.html\" title=\"Display the information about the Uniface configuration.\">/who</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__section_ov1_qw1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d950463e142\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__ul_iby_qw1_dcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d54065e1_d54066e1_d54067e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ArchiveFile</var>—existing UAR to\n               split into separate UARs</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d54068e1_d54069e1_d54070e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$RSO</code>—use the resources output\n               path (as specified by the $RSO logical) as the source of objects to put into\n               UARs.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d54071e1_d54072e1_d54073e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Options</var>—settings that specify\n               the type of objects to package, and the location of the resulting UAR files.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__section_qvd_sw1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d950463e166\">Options</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__1\">Options</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-components</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__2\">Put application components and startup shells\n                        from the specified source into <span class=\"ph filepath\">components.uar</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-global</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__2\">Put global objects from the specified source\n                        into archive files.<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__ul_mqr_sw1_dcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d54074e1_d54075e1_d54076e1\">Menus, messages, and formats into <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Lan</var>.uar</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d54077e1_d54078e1_d54079e1\">Glyphs into <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Lan</var>@gly.uar</span>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__li_d54080e1_d54081e1_d54082e1\">Other global objects into <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>.uar</span>\n</li>\n</ul></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-references</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__2\">Put descriptors, signatures, and DTD references\n                        from the specified source into <span class=\"ph filepath\">references.uar</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-objects</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__2\">Put components, global objects, and descriptors\n                        from the specified source into archive files; combines\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-components</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-global</span>, and\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-references</span>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-path=</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentPath</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__2\">Put compiled components located in the\n                        specified directory into an archive file.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-noUpdate</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18659e1_d18660e1_d18661e1__entry__2\">Display the operations and their results, but\n                        do not actually perform the operation.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__section_n5z_vw1_dcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d950463e317\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">split</span> operation creates one or more archive files based on\n            library and language.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Archive Files Created by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">urm split</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__1\">Object Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__2\">File Name</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__1\">Descriptors, signatures, and DTD\n                        references</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">references.uar</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__1\">Glyphs</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Lan</var>@gly.uar</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__1\">Menus, messages, and formats</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>@<var class=\"keyword varname\">Lan</var>.uar</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__1\">Other global objects</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Library</var>.uar</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__1\">Components and startup shells</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pzz1665702659433__table_d18662e1_d18663e1_d18664e1__entry__2\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">components.uar</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531160\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531160\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "urm split Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Creates one or more archive files based on object, library, and language. urm { Switches } split ArchiveFile | $RSO { Options } Switches /asn /dir $log /plg /pri /who Parameters ArchiveFile —existing UAR to split into separate UARs $RSO —use the resources output path (as specified by the $RSO logical) as the source of objects to put into UARs. Options —settings that specify the type of objects to package, and the location of the resulting UAR files. Options Options Description -components Put application components and startup shells from the specified source into components.uar . -global Put global objects from the specified source into archive files. Menus, messages, and formats into Library @ Lan .uar Glyphs into Library @ Lan @gly.uar Other global objects into Library .uar -references Put descriptors, signatures, and DTD references from the specified source into references.uar . -objects Put components, global objects, and descriptors from the specified source into archive files; combines -components , -global , and -references . -path= ComponentPath Put compiled components located in the specified directory into an archive file. -noUpdate Display the operations and their results, but do not actually perform the operation. Description The split operation creates one or more archive files based on library and language. Table 1. Archive Files Created by urm split Object Type File Name Descriptors, signatures, and DTD references references.uar Glyphs Library @ Lan @gly.uar Menus, messages, and formats Library @ Lan .uar Other global objects Library .uar Components and startup shells components.uar Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}